                    "value": "<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> to <span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The ort mob claws at all enemies in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] (@Check[reflex|dc:19|basic] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d6+1)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d6+5)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d6+6)[slashing]|options:area-damage] damage</p>"
